Package: aisdk.datatools
Title: Charting and Reporting Tools for the 'aisdk' Toolkit
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Yonghe", "Xia", , "xiayh17@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Heavy-dependency charting and reporting tools for the 'aisdk'
    toolkit: a structured 'ggplot2' chart schema and renderer, a 'knitr'-based
    AI reporting engine, and artifact generation. The package registers a
    'ggplot' JSON coercion handler with the core serializer on load, so 'aisdk'
    stays free of 'ggplot2'/'knitr' dependencies unless this package is used.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Imports: aisdk (>= 1.4.12), rlang, jsonlite, tools, utils
Suggests: ggplot2, knitr, rmarkdown, withr, R6, curl, testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
URL: https://github.com/YuLab-SMU/aisdk.datatools
BugReports: https://github.com/YuLab-SMU/aisdk.datatools/issues
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
